# Risk Assessment and Mitigation Plan

| Risk ID | Likelihood | Impact | Priority  | Mitigation Strategy |
|---------|------------|--------|-----------|----------------------|
| R1      | Medium     | High   | High      | Implement a geolocation API and test matching accuracy rigorously. |
| R2      | High       | Medium | High      | Conduct daily stand-up meetings and use Slack or Teams for communication. |
| R3      | Medium     | Medium | Medium    | Clearly define project scope in the charter and prioritize features with stakeholders. |
| R4      | High       | High   | Critical  | Conduct security audits and implement data encryption protocols. |
